children.value: Powered by hardware and software, the Smart Pantry will allow its users to track food items stored in their kitchen pantry. The principal component of the Smart Pantry will be this phone application, which will:
-Track items stored in a pantry at any given time
-Notify users when a food item is running low (based on the weight of that food item)
-Allow a user to add an item to the pantry by scanning its barcode or manually adding the information
-Remove a food item from the pantry on the app (when it has run out or is no longer wanted)
